songs.title: Thank u, next (Jennifer Coolidge and Ariana Grande conversation)
songs.lyrics:
-thank u, next instrumental-

Ariana:
I mean, he was really cute, you know?
He was really cute.

Jennifer:
Yeah.

Ariana:
And it was, it was really big.

Jennifer:
Well, I've only gone out with one guy that had a big front tooth.
And I liked it, 'cause it, he never got anything stuck in the front teeth.
But, have you ever gone out with someone that had no teeth at all?

Ariana:
No.
